Files repartition:

*******************************************************************************
/apps/px/bin/
*******************************************************************************
All the runnable scripts

px          : Send a command (start, stop, reload, status) to all receivers and senders
pxReceiver  : Send a command (start, stop, reload, status) to a particular receiver
pxSender    : Send a command (start, stop, reload, status) to a particular sender

paplat      : Used to make latencies stats
pxChecker   : Restart a sender/receiver that should be running (cron each minute)
pxDBCleaner : Keep a certain amount of days in DB (cron each day)

*******************************************************************************
/apps/px/etc/
*******************************************************************************
Configuration files for senders and receivers are
put there

/apps/px/etc/rx/titi.conf  (example for a receiver)
/apps/px/etc/tx/toto.conf  (example for a sender)
header2client.conf (direct routing file)

*******************************************************************************
/apps/px/[r,t]xq/
*******************************************************************************
Reception queues:     apps/px/rxq/titi/  (example for a source titi)
Transmission queues:  apps/px/txq/toto/3/2005110815/ (example for a client toto)

*******************************************************************************
/apps/px/db/
*******************************************************************************
The database.

The file SAUY_SUMU_280100_00005:nws-alph:SUMU:SA:5:Direct:20051107210952
will be put in /apps/px/db/20051107/SA/nws-alph/SUMU/

*******************************************************************************
/apps/px/log/
*******************************************************************************
Log files.

Log of source titi: /apps/px/log/rx_titi.log
Log of client toto: /apps/px/log/tx_toto.log

*******************************************************************************
